<html>
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title><%= title %></title>
        <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans:400,700&display=swap&subset=greek" rel="stylesheet">
        <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/131c23bef3.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/polites-submit.css">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/bootstrap.css">
        <script src="../js/jquery-3.4.1.min.js"></script>
        <script src="../js/bootstrap.js"></script>   
    </head>
    <body>
        <nav class="navbar navbar-light bg-light" id="index-navbar-logo">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">
              <i class="fas fa-head-side-mask"></i>
              Ψηφιακή καταγραφή COVID-19
            </a>
        </nav>


        <div class="jumbotron jumbotron-fluid message-polites">
            <div class="container">
              <h1 class="display-4">Επιβεβαίωση στοιχείων</h1>
            </div>
        </div>
        <h4>Σας έχουμε αποστείλει έναν κωδικό επαλήθευσης στην διεύθυνση email σας και στο κινητό σας με sms</h2><br>

        <% if (error){ %>
        <div class="alert alert-danger polites-register-errors" role="alert">
            <%= error %>
        </div>
        <% } %>


        <div class="container">
            <form action="" method="POST">
                
                <div class="row">
                    <% if (verifyemail != null) { %>
                        <div class="col-sm-6">
                          <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-body">
                              <h5 class="card-title">Επαλήθευση email</h5>
                              <p class="card-text"><%= verifyemail %></p>
                            
                              <div class="input-group mb-2 mr-sm-2">
                                <div class="input-group-prepend">
                                  <div class="input-group-text"><i class="fas fa-key"></i></div>
                                </div>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" name="email-code-input-verify" placeholder="Username">
                              </div>
                          
                            </div>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                    <% }else { %>
                        <div class="col-sm-6">
                            <div class="card">
                              <div class="card-body">
                                <h5 class="card-title">Επαλήθευση email</h5>
                                <p class="card-text" style="font-size: 40px;"><i class="fas fa-user-check"></i></p>
                              </div>
                            </div>
                          </div>

                    <% } %>
                    
                    <% if (verifyphone != null) { %>
                        <div class="col-sm-6">
                          <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-body">
                              <h5 class="card-title">Επαλήθευση κινητού</h5>
                              <p class="card-text"><%= verifyphone %></p>
                            
                              <div class="input-group mb-2 mr-sm-2">
                                <div class="input-group-prepend">
                                  <div class="input-group-text"><i class="fas fa-key"></i></div>
                                </div>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" name="phone-code-input-verify" placeholder="Username">
                              </div>
                          
                            </div>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                    <% }else { %>
                        <div class="col-sm-6">
                            <div class="card">
                              <div class="card-body">
                                <h5 class="card-title">Επαλήθευση κινητού</h5>
                                <p class="card-text" style="font-size: 40px;"><i class="fas fa-user-check"></i></p>
                              </div>
                            </div>
                          </div>

                    <% } %>
                </div>
                <br>

                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" name="verify-now"><i class="fas fa-satellite"></i> Επαλήθευση</button>

            </form>
            
        </div>
   
          
    </body>
</html>